high_descs: Turn left and then right to stand on the right side of the toilet.
Pick the middle bottle up from the back of the toilet.
Move to the left a bit and face the surface behind the tub.
Put the bottle down on the surface behind the tub.
Turn to face the back of the toilet again.
Pick the bottle on the right side of the toilet up.
Move to the left a bit to face the surface behind the tub.
Put the bottle down on the surface behind the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put two bottles down behind the tub in a bathroom.

high_descs: Turn left then head to the right side of the toilet
Pick up the middle spray bottle on the tank
Turn left then head to the tub counter
Put the spray bottle on the left side of the tub counter
Turn right then  face the toilet tank
Pick up the spray bottle on the tank
Turn left then face the tub counter
Put the spray bottle beside the other one on the tub counter
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottle on the tub counter

high_descs: turn left, go to right side of toilet on the right
pick up purple bottle in between other purple bottles
face counter to the right of bathtub
place purple bottle to the right of the right end of bathtub
go to right side of toilet
pick up purple bottle on right side of toilet
face counter to the right of bathtub
place bottle to the right of purple bottle
anns.task_desc: place two purple bottles on counter to the right of bathtub
